  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレら、今までけっこう金使ったよな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We've sure spent a good amount of money, huh.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37544</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そっか、
そういえばそうだね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh...Now that you mention it, we have.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37920</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その金を戦うためと違くて、
貯金してたら、オレら今ごろ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If we didn't spend those money for fighting,
and instead saved it, we'd be...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38376</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_004</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも戦わなかったら
お金も入ってこなかったよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But we won't have money if we didn't fight.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38828</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぐあ〜っ！　そっか、今からでも
ごーゆーできると思ったのに！　ごーゆーっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aghh!! You're right! Until now I thought I could
finally retire in peace! Ugh!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>not exact</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_006</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もう最初から全部間違ってるよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You've always had the wrong idea since the start...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40072</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_007</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>よっし！　ここまで貯まった記念に
ぱーっと使おうぜっ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Alright! We should use up everything we've
saved in commemoration of today's achievement!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41436</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_008</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おおっ！　マジで！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>R-Really? We can!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42116</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今日は贅沢に超高級レストランだね！
どーせ敵を倒して得たあぶく銭！　使ってナンボ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I guess we'll have dinner in the fanciest restaurant in town tonight. 
Why worry? We can just earn it back again from our enemies.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43224</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>だ、ダメですッ！！
まったく、なんですか、もう！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>W-We cant! Nope! I forbid it!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44972</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;ちゃん、お顔が怖いってば♪</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aww, you should've seen your face. &lt;Mel&gt;!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>45480</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>な、なぁ、ちょっとくらいはよくないか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>H-Hey, why don't we spend a little bit?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46464</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>は、ははははは。
ウソだよウソ！　マジにとんなよ〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ahahahah...I'm kidding, kidding.
Don't glare at me like that...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47712</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VCT_006_208_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;……恐ろしい子！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Darn, &lt;Mel&gt; can really get scary!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
